<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,153,539]" box="[199,564,512,539]" pageId="6" pageNumber="272">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,353,512,539]" pageId="6" pageNumber="272">Distribution.</emphasis>
Palaearctic: 
